creator: Famly ApS
descriptionHtml:
Our Bright Horizons Family app is a safe and secure way to keep families connected to your child’s nursery day. You can stay updated with their daily activities, see what they have been learning and get status updates including daily activities, room locations and more through our handy activity log. You’ll even receive photos and videos of your little one, so you can be sure they’re happy.

The app also features two-way communication between you and your child’s nursery, enabling a variety of functions:
· See your child’s daily activity and access learning journeys
· Message the nursery, answer permissions or notify pick up changes

Please note: Some features mentioned are currently in development and there will be additional functionality available in the future.
Bright Horizons Family UK is a GDPR-compliant digital platform.
